    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended primarily for parts or as a major restoration project. The body has extensive rust, particularly along the door sills and rear quarter panels, and the clear coat is peeling significantly on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears in the seats and a cracked dashboard. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a noticeable knock, the transmission shifts harshly, and it will require immediate work to be roadworthy. It is being sold strictly as-is with no warranties implied.",
