    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-standard condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, reflects a standard of care that is truly unrivaled. Mechanically absolute and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection. This is not merely a pre-owned vehicle; it is a definitive statement in excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
