    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, while the interior remains pristine with the original factory scent and supple, untouched upholstery. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates flawlessly, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history. It has been strictly garage-kept under a climate-controlled cover, ensuring the chassis and engine bay are as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning inspection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
