    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, reflecting a standard of maintenance that is seldom observed in the secondary market. Every facet\u2014from the flawless exterior contours to the pristine, untouched interior surfaces\u2014demonstrates meticulous stewardship. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision of a new factory delivery. For the discerning buyer who accepts no compromises, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle preserved in its absolute prime.",
