      "description": "Hey there! I'm so excited to share this absolute gem with you. It\u2019s in gorgeous, pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it drives like a total dream. If you're looking for something that's practically brand new and ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Drop me a message if you want to take a look!",
