      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a meticulously maintained Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains rigid, supported by a factory-spec limited-slip differential and flawless suspension geometry. No rod bearing issues or VANOS rattle; comprehensive service logs included. The exterior retains its factory depth with zero paint correction required, while the interior displays no bolster wear or pixel degradation. A turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
